      • getNamespaces

        public Map<String,String> getNamespaces()
                                 throws IllegalStateException
        Description copied from interface: Session
        Returns the modifiable namespace map of this Session. The map is backed by the default mappings of Data#getNamespaceMap(). New mappings are stored in the Session map and may override the default mappings. Removal of mappings is performed on the Session map, and may reactivate the default mapping as a consequence.
        Specified by:
        getNamespaces in interface Session

      • close

        public void close()
        Description copied from interface: Session
        Closes the Session instance, releasing any resource possibly allocated. Calling this method additional times has no effect. After this method is called, calls to other method of the Session interface will result in IllegalStateExceptions to be thrown.
        Specified by:
